name: BetaPro Canadian Gold Miners 2x Daily Bull ETF
longDescription: GDXU seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to two times (200 percent) the daily performance of the Solactive Canadian Gold Miners Index. GDXU does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
